{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"147","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"COP23後全球之因應策略及發展研討會","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/51.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 468px;' /></p>\n\n<p style='color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: inherit; font-size: 16px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;'>為將聯合國氣候變化綱要公約第23屆締約方會議(UNFCCC COP 23)會後第一手資訊提供給國人，並分享全球減碳策略新知，台灣永續能源研究基金會將舉辦「COP23後全球之因應策略及發展」研討會，期望產、官、學、研與公民社會與時俱進，並對未來趨勢之因應做好準備。</p>\n\n<p style='color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: inherit; font-size: 16px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;'>本課程邀請台灣永續能源研究基金會簡又新董事長、台灣綜合研究院蘇漢邦所長、國際氣候發展智庫(ICDI)趙恭岳執行長、環境品質文教基金會謝英士董事長、台達文教基金會張揚乾副執行長、高雄市政府環境保護局&hellip;&hellip;等，從COP23帶回來的第一手即時資訊。</p>\n\n<ul style='color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: inherit; font-size: 16px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em 3em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial;'>\n\t<li style='box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;'>主辦單位：台灣永續能源研究基金會(TAISE)、台灣企業永續研訓中心(CCS)&nbsp;</li>\n\t<li style='box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;'>指導單位：中華民國 外交部</li>\n\t<li style='box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;'>實施對象：會員企業優先，歡迎專業人士、對「COP23後全球之因應策略及發展」議題有興趣之民眾或學生</li>\n\t<li style='box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;'>活動日期：2017年12月07日（星期四）14時至17時。(13:30開始報到)</li>\n\t<li style='box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;'>活動地點：外交部外交及國際事務學院7樓共同教室（四）(台北市大安區敦化南路一段106號7樓)</li>\n\t<li style='box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;'>報名費用：免費</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;'><a href='https://www.surveycake.com/s/Opl6v'>https://www.surveycake.com/s/Opl6v</a></p>\n\n<p style='box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;'><span pro='' sans='' source='' style='color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: '>聯絡方式：蔡先生 電話：(02) 2769-8968 #206 / EMAIL:&nbsp;</span><a href='mailto:shiny@ccstw.net' style='color: royalblue; text-decoration-line: none; font-family: inherit; font-size: 16px; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; box-sizing: border-box; background: transparent; border: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;'>shiny@ccstw.net</a><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<table pro='' sans='' source='' style='color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: '>\n\t<tbody style='box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit; margin: 0px; outline: 0px; padding: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;'>\n\t\t<tr style='box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; font-famil